main event: A UFO sighting was reported near Fairborn, Ohio on 8/12/1969.
interesting points: The observation was made at 3:00 AM EDT., The reported object was described as round and bright, moving in an arc., The witness observed the phenomenon from a mile east of Fairborn, Ohio., Though a detailed questionnaire was provided for gathering information, many sections were marked with 'N/A' indicating insufficient data., The conclusion of the investigation was that there was 'Insufficient Data' to ascertain what the object was.
sighted object: round, bright light that moved upward and downward in an arc
witness description: Civilian observation, no detailed witness profile provided.
